%h1 Find and Replace

%p Enter a query to find all occurrences of an exact (case-sensitive) string in page content. You will then be able to replace those occurrences with another string.

- form_tag(new_admin_replacement_path, :method => :get) do
  %table.fieldset{:cellpadding=>0, :cellspacing=>0, :border=>0}
    %tr
      %th.label
        = label_tag "q", "Find:"
      %td
        = text_field_tag "q", params[:q], :size => '15', :alt => "search", :class => "textbox"
  %p.buttons
    %input{:type => "submit", :value => "Find"}
    or
    = link_to 'Cancel', admin_pages_path